{"tid":751528,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波網誌批美國一力發動開倒車　料對港影響更急更廣","createTime":"2018-07-22T03:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:54:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5713184c49d34b912e19ba87525656be3a7b0e98","tid":751528,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180722/s00001/7eb347cae079e807fe7cade9db9901e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180722%2Fs00001%2F7eb347cae079e807fe7cade9db9901e7.jpg&h=7c4faeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰升溫，本港財政司長陳茂波於網誌批評，今次國際貿易爭端是「美國一力發動」、「大開倒車」，呼籲美國負責任地處理貿易糾紛，盡快返回雙邊洽談，「這樣才符合世界廣大民眾的根本利益」。他又說，本港經濟明年面對的直接和間接影響或會「來得更快、更廣泛」，但有信心香港金融系統能夠承受潛在衝擊，外界毋須過分擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n網誌題為＜嚴陣以待　防範風險＞，陳茂波指，事情的發展已拖累年初原本全面向好的環球經濟氣氛，使經濟前景變得極不明朗。他估計，這次貿易磨擦還會持續一段時間，外圍環境下行風險正顯著增加，政府不會掉以輕心，會繼續「密切跟蹤事態發展」，做好應對預備。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波又說，中美貿易磨擦升溫，為金融市場帶來不明朗因素，股市將更趨波動，但有信心香港金融系統能夠承受潛在衝擊，「大家毋須過分擔憂」，「在金融安全這個範疇，香港是有信心、有經驗、有能力應對貿易戰帶來的挑戰」。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波最後提到，這次美國在國際貿易上「大開倒車」，對世界經濟前景帶來十分不利影響，「我們和世界很多地區和國家都一樣，期望美國負責任地處理貿易糾紛，盡快返回雙邊洽談，並透過世貿機制解決矛盾，這樣才符合世界廣大民眾的根本利益」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180722/s00001/1532225904648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180722%2Fs00001%2F1532225904648&d=kPCBNtvCMKakj9SM%2F161SgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=cf92c541\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180722%2Fs00001%2F1532225904648&h=4ae0799d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180722/s00001/1532225904648</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fso.gov.hk/chi/blog/blog220718.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fso.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fblog%2Fblog220718.htm&d=kPCBNtvCMKakj9SM%2F161SgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=d43ac861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fso.gov.hk/chi/blog/blog220718.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d86b56e41a29f92d9e78d7175ad258727ee4cee8","tid":751528,"uid":3020,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"只為刷鞋"},{"pid":"002718754502c9711a3457be020ed4dd6ec8956a","tid":751528,"uid":76470,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"挑，驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中国都未亮劍<br />\n只要一亮劍就會成為最大贏家啊<br />\n洗撚你呢個區區一個特別行政區嘅財爺係到鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641b359094ca98189cda93f9e46eadde832e9986","tid":751528,"uid":132859,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"搵人係twitter tag俾trump trump睇下條友有幾大言不慚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f50af0d7280f660c5f959d63138c42d3ce8eab1","tid":751528,"uid":30215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:07:54.000Z","msg":"依班撚樣對電動車開倒車呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a184dd436ccccdf5b4353a2df342f9b7760665c9","tid":751528,"uid":8048,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"強烈要求一眾高官/家人表演剪綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124e073464f706860be2f53a73370c0c75c95467","tid":751528,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a184dd436ccccdf5b4353a2df342f9b7760665c9","tid":751528,"uid":8048,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:10:23.0